            AssessIQ vs iMocha
          </span>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ── HERO ── -->
  <section class="bg-aiq-bg-base border-b border-aiq-border">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-aiq-xl py-aiq-4xl">

      <p class="font-mono text-aiq-xs text-aiq-fg-muted tracking-aiq-mono uppercase mb-aiq-lg m-0">
        Compare &middot; Updated May 2026
      </p>

      <h1 class="font-serif text-aiq-3xl sm:text-aiq-hero font-normal tracking-aiq-tighter text-aiq-fg-primary leading-[1.05] mb-aiq-xl mt-0 max-w-3xl">
        AssessIQ vs iMocha: Complete 2026 Comparison
      </h1>

      <!-- 50-word TL;DR — snippet target per §5.3 -->
      <div class="bg-aiq-bg-raised border border-aiq-border rounded-aiq-lg p-aiq-xl mb-aiq-2xl max-w-2xl">
        <p class="font-mono text-aiq-xs text-aiq-fg-muted tracking-aiq-mono uppercase mb-aiq-sm mt-0">TL;DR</p>
        <p class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed m-0">
          iMocha's Skills Intelligence Cloud maps skills gaps across your entire workforce — from hiring through L&D and internal mobility — at enterprise scale. AssessIQ focuses on structured pre-employment screening for Indian IT companies: coding tests, rubric scoring, and a straightforward admin workflow. Different scopes for different organizational needs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Internal links row -->
      <p class="font-sans text-aiq-sm text-aiq-fg-muted leading-relaxed m-0">
        Also compare: <a href="/compare/assessiq-vs-mettl" class="text-aiq-accent hover:text-aiq-accent-hover underline underline-offset-2">AssessIQ vs Mercer Mettl</a> &middot; <a href="/compare/assessiq-vs-hackerearth" class="text-aiq-accent hover:text-aiq-accent-hover underline underline-offset-2">AssessIQ vs HackerEarth</a> &middot; <a href="/alternatives/imocha" class="text-aiq-accent hover:text-aiq-accent-hover underline underline-offset-2">iMocha alternatives</a>
