            </li>
            <li class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Your use case extends beyond hiring into L&D, internal mobility, and upskilling — and you need a single platform to connect those workflows.
            </li>
            <li class="font-sans text-aiq-md text-aiq-fg-secondary leading-relaxed">
